Subject: Q4 2024 Financial Report and Investment Update
From: marketing@techstartup.com
To: investors@venturecapital.com
Date: Tue Jan 16 2024 00:00:00 GMT+0530 (India Standard Time)

documents.text: I hope this email finds you well. I'm writing to provide you with our Q4 2024 financial report and update you on our recent progress.

FINANCIAL HIGHLIGHTS:
- Revenue: $2.5M (up 40% from Q3)
- Gross Margin: 65%
- Operating Expenses: $1.8M
- Net Profit: $425,000
- Cash Position: $3.2M

- Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC): $150
- Customer Lifetime Value (LTV): $2,400
- Monthly Recurring Revenue (MRR): $850,000
- Churn Rate: 3.2%

BUSINESS UPDATES:
1. Product Launch: Successfully launched our AI-powered analytics platform
2. Team Expansion: Hired 15 new employees across engineering and sales
3. Partnership: Signed strategic partnership with Microsoft Azure
4. Funding: Completed Series B round raising $15M
